# Demo & SEO

Reference: `demo/index.html` — follow existing **page zone** and **section card** patterns.

## Page layout (v1.3+)

Four labeled zones in `#main-content`, each with `.zone-header` (label + title + desc):

| Zone id | Purpose |
|---|---|
| `#overview` | Why choose Shutters (accordion content) |
| `#demos` | Interactive feature demos |
| `#comparisons` | Motion Lab + library comparisons |
| `#documentation` | How-to-use guide with snippet tabs |

- Individual blocks: `.section-card` inside `.page-zone` (spacing via `.page-zone > .section-card`)
- Hero: `.version-badge`, `.package-links` (GitHub + npm icons), `.page-nav` anchor pills
- Demo-only UI: `demo/shutters-demo-ui.js` (copy buttons, framework tabs, CDN SRI, motion lab)

## HTML accordion markup

Authors omit ARIA — JS adds it. Required classes: `shutters-accordion`, `shutters-item`, `shutters-header`, `shutters-title`, `shutters-icon`, `shutters-content`, `shutters-body`.

## Init pattern

```html
<script type="module">
  import { ShuttersAccordion } from './shutters-core.js';
  import { initAll } from './shutters-auto.js';
  import { initDemoUi } from './shutters-demo-ui.js';

  new ShuttersAccordion({
    container: '.shutters-accordion:not([data-shutters])',
    animationDuration: 350,
    animationEasing: 'cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1)',
    defaultOpen: 'none'
  });
  initAll();
  initDemoUi();
</script>
```

- **Never** load `shutters-core.js` twice (no duplicate script tag + import)
- `[data-shutters]` containers use `initAll()` only — exclude from manual instance selector

## SEO blocks in demo/index.html

- Primary meta, Open Graph, Twitter Card, favicon
- JSON-LD: `SoftwareSourceCode` + `FAQPage` + `HowTo` + `BreadcrumbList`
- Update JSON-LD `version` and `.version-badge` on release (`npm run version:sync`)

## Build & deploy

- Dev: `npm run dev` or `npm run dev:demo`
- Production: `npm run build:demo` → `dist-demo/`
- GitHub Pages base: `/shutters-accordion/demo/` (`vite.config.demo.js`)
- Deploy: push to `main`/`master` triggers `.github/workflows/deploy-demo.yml`
- Pre-build: `npm run sri` refreshes `demo/cdn-integrity.json`

